docs.snippet: BUENOS AIRES, March 15. -- The League of Nations Chaco Commission has taken a first step to put on the American nations instead of the League of Nations the responsibility for failure of the peace negotiations which the League commission took away...
docs.lead_paragraph: BUENOS AIRES, March 15. -- The League of Nations Chaco Commission has taken a first step to put on the American nations instead of the League of Nations the responsibility for failure of the peace negotiations which the League commission took away from the Pan-American Conference at a moment when success seemed within easy reach.

headline.main: CHACO FAILURE LAID AT AMERICA'S DOOR; League Body Says New World Will Have to Use Force to Terminate War. PEACE ONCE SEEMED NEAR But the Pan-American Conference Yielded Arbitration Role to Geneva's Commission.

docs.lead_paragraph: The movement of the dollar was extremely narrow last week, based on the quotation for the French franc. Trading was light throughout. Highest price for the week was 100.9 cents and the lowest 100.6 cents, with the close at 100.8 cents, unchanged from the preceding week.
